Merge pull request #44 from livinginthepast/command-dispatch

Dispatch commands as classes

Dispatch commands as classes

instead of `_`-prefixed methods, in part to shrink the `FakeFtp::Server`
class, and also to allow for a less conflict-prone contribution process.
